REGRESSION - org.hck.enums.TestCategoryType
 
retry(ITestResult) - Method in class org.hck.listners.RetryFailedTests
Automatically retries a test for a set number of times before failing a test if ConfigProperties.RETRYFAILEDTESTS is set to "yes".
RetryFailedTests - Class in org.hck.listners
RetryFailedTests class automatically invokes the retry analyzer to determine if TestNG can retry a test case again in an attempt to see if the test that just fails now passes.
